<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV7">
<l>oṉṟiraṇṭu mūrttiyā yuṟakkamōṭu ṇarcciyāy</l>
<l>oṉṟiraṇṭu kālamāki vēlaiñāla māyiṉāy</l>
<l>oṉṟiraṇṭu tīyumāki yāyaṉāya māyaṉē</l>
<l>oṉṟiraṇṭu kaṇṇiṉāṉu muṉṉaiyētta vallaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Taking one plus two forms, being sleep as well as wakefulness,</l>
<l>being [the lord of] the three [periods of] time,</l>
<l>being the earth [surrounded by] the ocean,</l>
<l>being the three fires, O dark [Lord] who became a cowherd!</l>
<l>Can even the three-eyed [Śiva] praise You?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
